# Cloud Harbor — Environment Variables
#
# Cloud Harbor uses the free Open-Meteo API, which requires no API key
# and works for every city in the world out of the box.
# (https://open-meteo.com — no signup required)
#
# If you want to swap in OpenWeatherMap instead, see src/services/weatherApi.ts
# and add VITE_OPENWEATHER_API_KEY=your_key_here
